songs.title: Darling Nicki (Minaj)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Beyoncé]
I met this girl, named Nicki
I guess you could say, she was the rap queen
I met her in the studio lobby
But her booty look bigger in the magazines
She said, "Bey, would you jump in this song of mine?"
How could I resist?
When I heard little Nicki rhyme
